summary:
Okay I know nothing about Moomin all I know is I keep seeing all this shit about it. 
Purely from what I’ve seen: 
My first...
body:
Okay I know nothing about Moomin all I know is I keep seeing all this shit about it.

Purely from what I’ve seen:

My first impression of Snufkin was that he was a sweet soft forest man who only came in the fall.

Now I’m convinced that in a modern retelling Snufkin would be wearing a brown canvas jacket covered in patches that all ecology focused and anti establishment with maybe a couple simple leaves or a pride flag.

His hat is functional and not an aesthetic choice because who the fuck has time for aesthetics, and when he shows up he’s always all soft and nice with Moomin and quotes poetry and shit and is just super gay for his boyfriend.

But like when he’s not in this very small part of the woods where people can identify him he like covers his face with a fucking bandana and destroys companies and facilitates that are harming the environment and like takes back the land by fucking burning the buildings down (in a very controlled way) and cultivating endangered trees in places the plan to bulldoze.

And this little man just leads this fucking double life as a green vigilante that he doesn’t tell anyone about…
